-magazine/.premium/how-could-israels-army-abandon-this-kibbutz-for-seven-hours-on-october-7/0000018f-0076-db42-a99f-adff41440000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级官员：我们提出在人质交易第一阶段释放40名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/senior-hamas-official-we-offered-to-release-40-hostages-in-first-phase-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-0f68-dc39-a9cf-bfeeb1450000</link><description>这位官员在接受伦敦卡塔尔Al-Arabi Al-Jadid报纸采访时补充说，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔继续在加沙指挥该组织，据该官员称，甚至离开了他藏身的地道并在战斗中巡逻。地面以上区域</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:39:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/senior-hamas-official-we-offered-to-release-40-hostages-in-first-phase-of-hostage-deal/0000018f-0f68-dc39-a9cf-bfeeb1450000</guid></item><item><title>圣殿山活动人士因试图献祭山羊而被捕，赞扬本格维尔为释放山羊而进行的非法干预</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-activists-gloat-ben-gvirs-illegal-intervention-got-them-released-from-arrest/0000018f-0ef2-d0a8-a5ef-bff7cba50000</link><description>右翼活动人士赞扬国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）进行干预，释放了三名因打算在圣殿山宰杀山羊作为逾越节祭品而被拘留的嫌疑人，尽管高等法院禁止他干预警方的行动决定</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/right-wing-activists-gloat-ben-gvirs-illegal-intervention-got-them-released-from-arrest/0000018f-0ef2-d0a8-a5ef-bff7cba50000</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院通过法案向以色列提供数十亿美元援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0e69-d0a8-a5ef-bf6dfd190000</link><description>众议院周六批准该方案后，该法案以 79 票对 18 票的压倒性通过。拜登总统表示，今晚，参议院两党多数派与众议院一起响应历史在这个关键转折点的号召。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0e69-d0a8-a5ef-bf6dfd190000</guid></item><item><title>反坦克导弹摧毁以色列北部的两栋房屋后，以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的数十个目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-live/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0ddd-d6a0-a9ef-cddd5c300000</link><description>哈马斯高级官员：我们提出在第一阶段协议中释放 40 名人质，而不是 20 名人质 ■ 以色列国防军袭击加沙南部人道主义区内的火箭发射器 ■ 以色列军队动员两个预备役旅返回加沙南部行动 ■ 德国恢复与以色列的合作近东救济工程处</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-live/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0ddd-d6a0-a9ef-cddd5c300000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特官员担心以色列监狱长正在放宽犹太安全拘留者的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/prisons-chief-easing-jewish-security-inmates-terms/0000018f-0c6f-dc39-a9cf-bdeff5e00000</link><description>这些官员已联系以色列总检察长，表达对国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的助手、监狱管理局局长科比·雅科比的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/prisons-chief-easing-jewish-security-inmates-terms/0000018f-0c6f-dc39-a9cf-bdeff5e00000</guid></item><item><title>应内塔尼亚胡总理儿子的要求，希伯来语维基百科投票删除有关他的条目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-wikipedia-votes-to-remove-entry-on-pm-netanyahus-son-following-his-request/0000018f-0c51-df8a-afcf-af5b90320000</link><description>本月早些时候，以色列总理之子要求删除阿夫纳·内塔尼亚胡的条目，希伯来语维基百科编辑社区以 75 比 54 的投票结果将阿夫纳·内塔尼亚胡的页面合并到内塔尼亚胡家族的页面中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 19:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-wikipedia-votes-to-remove-entry-on-pm-netanyahus-son-following-his-request/0000018f-0c51-df8a-afcf-af5b90320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带北部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip/0000018f-0c24-df8a-afcf-af3ff5980000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，中士。一等