i-army-denies-claim-it-dug-mass-grave-in-gaza-says-it-searched-for-hostages-bodies/0000018f-09da-d6a0-a9ef-c9de6bea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队证实两名真主党高级成员在黎巴嫩被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-killing-of-two-senior-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018f-0b4d-d6a0-a9ef-cbddffe40000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，周二被杀的特工来自真主党防空系统和精锐的拉德万部队空中部队，并补充说，三架从黎巴嫩起飞的疑似敌对飞机在以色列北部上空被拦截</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-killing-of-two-senior-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018f-0b4d-d6a0-a9ef-cbddffe40000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令以色列-巴勒斯坦遇难者家庭论坛重返学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum-back-in-to-schools/0000018f-0a2d-db42-a99f-afbf8fe20000</link><description>耶路撒冷地方法院法官亚伯拉罕·鲁宾批评教育部禁止“家长圈 - 家庭论坛”在以色列学校运营，尽管没有对右翼组织对其提出的“指控进行适当的事实审查”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum-back-in-to-schools/0000018f-0a2d-db42-a99f-afbf8fe20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，以色列没有提供证据证明近东救济工程处在加沙的工作人员属于恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</link><description>对该机构“中立性”的独立审查与对以色列声称 12 名工作人员参与 10 月 7 日袭击的调查是分开进行的</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院通过法案向以色列提供数十亿美元援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</link><description>以色列国防军说中士。 42 岁一等兵 Salm Alkreshat 于周一在战斗中身亡 ■ 布林肯计划访问沙特阿拉伯参加世界经济论坛 ■ 以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚居民撤离 ■ 美国指定两家伊朗公司，四人受到网络制裁 ■ 美国官员称，加沙地区，特别是北部地区，饥荒风险“非常高” ■ 数百名示威者封锁特拉维夫以色列国防军总部外的道路，呼吁释放人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡家前举行逾越节家宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</link><description>逾越节前夕，数百人呼吁释放凯撒利亚的人质。一名亲戚向内塔尼亚胡呼喊，“在自由的节日里，有 133 名犹太公民被哈马斯囚禁，释放我们，这样我们就能有一位勇敢的领导人来达成协议”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军情报主管因 10 月 7 日的失败而辞职，这对其他以色列国防领导人来说变成了沙漏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦是哈马斯大屠杀后下台的最高级官员，他无法预测他继续担任以色列军队情报部门负责人会造成多么严重的内部危机，也无法预测他会成为右翼分子的目标极端分子</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</guid></item><item><title>美国不应该制裁一个流氓营，而应该关注内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</link><description>如果谴责极端正统的内扎·耶胡达以色列国防军营的“莱希法”涉及约旦河西岸的侵犯人权行为，那么以色列的整个政治梯队都需要承担责任。美国应该明确地说</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</guid></item></channel></rss>